tellraw @a {"text": "It is done.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "The purge is history.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "The flame of this land will dwindle and die...", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "But, hopefully, it's dying breaths will be all that are needed to save the world.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "For a time now, everyone will be safe.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "When the next day of judgement arrives, perhaps everyone will have already saved themselves from it.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "In E'Siraph, that was not so...", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "But the power was had, and the choice was made.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Their fate sealed by their own wills.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Mercy for the few, or salvation for the masses?", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "I always said the choice was easy.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "But, perhaps, the options aren't as clear as such I pose.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "In any case, I am quite pleased with you and your choice.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "However, we still have one last problem to solve: You.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "You and your immortality, it cannot be allowed to persist.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Goodbye, wise one.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "This shall be the last you hear from us.", "color": "white", "italic": true}